         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[…] ¶  ¶ I do myself the honour to acknowledge the rect ¶  of your highly interesting letters of the 12 of Feby. and the accompanying documents placed in my hands for perusal by Dr. Mueller last week ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">65.03.02</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">Redmond Barry to [Jaspar Friedrich Kern]</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">VPRS 830/PO/1, Redmond Barry outward letter book, [<seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Library</seg>], Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof. notes by RH.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>[…]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">not relevant text omitted?</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I do myself the honour to acknowledge the rect<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>receipt.</p>
               </note> of your highly interesting letters of the 12 of Feby. and the accompanying documents placed in my hands for perusal by Dr. Mueller last week wh. I have returned to him — I must be allowed to express my admiration of the zeal and philanthropic spirit in which you propose to enter in the undertaking you explain […]<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This is apparently about a scheme to provide schooling for children living in remote locations.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">[R. Barry]<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition,</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
